title: Smac 2.7 beta for Vista and Windows 7
description:
Improved Compatibility for VISTA and Windows 2008 - Fully Compatible to VISTA (32-bit and 64-bit), Windows 2008 (32-bit and 64-bit)
       
    *

      Improved Internalization! - Fully functional in all non-English Windows environment
       
    *

      Capability to delete MAC Address Change log
       
    *

      Capability to delete MAC Address Change History (Recently Changed List)








        If you are worried about using the keygen use this: 

              SMC2U-00C8-0004-0467-B30B-00005DE7
